OL,3,CMan connected to 'Putney Pusher'
OL,4,Cincident rearrested for drug possession
OL,6,FWatch: The moment a jogger appears to
OL,7,Fpush a woman in front of a bus on
OL,8,FPutney Bridge in 2017
OL,10,FThe man arrested under suspicion of
OL,11,Fbeing the "Putney Pusher" has been
OL,12,Frearrested for suspected possession of
OL,13,FClass A drugs.
OL,15,FThe 2017 incident shocked the public,
OL,16,Fwith footage showing a bus swerve out
OL,17,Fof the way after the 33-year-old
OL,18,Fvictim was pushed into the road. She
OL,19,Fescaped with minor injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
