PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781722095
OL,3,CMan connected to 'Putney Pusher'
OL,4,Cincident rearrested for drug possession
OL,6,FA man was arrested in connection with
OL,7,Fthe incident on Monday, years after
OL,8,Fpolice gave up on the case, despite an
OL,9,Fextensive investigation.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, the same man was
OL,12,Frearrested for possession of Class A
OL,13,Fand Class B drugs.
OL,15,FPolice said in a statement: "On
OL,16,FMonday, 15 June, a 44-year-old man was
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,18,Fgrievous bodily harm.
OL,26,@wD@]OU
