OL,3,CMan connected to 'Putney Pusher'
OL,4,Cincident rearrested for drug possession
OL,6,F"The arrest relates to an incident on
OL,7,F5 May 2017, where a woman was pushed
OL,8,Finto the path of a bus on Putney
OL,9,FBridge in Putney.
OL,11,F"Once in police custody, he was also
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of possession of
OL,13,FClass A and Class B drugs.
OL,15,F"He has since been bailed pending
OL,16,Ffurther investigation in relation to
OL,17,Fall offences. Enquiries continue."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
