OL,3,CMan connected to 'Putney Pusher'
OL,4,Cincident rearrested for drug possession
OL,6,FIt was reported at the time that 15
OL,7,Fminutes later the jogger appeared on
OL,8,Fthe other side of the bridge, running
OL,9,Fin the opposite direction.
OL,11,FThe victim tried to speak to him but
OL,12,Fhe did not acknowledge her and carried
OL,13,Fon running.
OL,15,FThe runner was described as white,
OL,16,Faged early to mid 30s, with brown eyes
OL,17,Fand short brown hair.
OL,19,FWhile detectives interviewed 50 men
OL,20,Fand arrested three suspects at the
OL,21,Ftime, no one was ever charged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
