OL,3,CMan connected to 'Putney Pusher'
OL,4,Cincident rearrested for drug possession
OL,6,FThe investigation was closed in 2018,
OL,7,Fbut the arrest was made on Monday
OL,8,Fafter new information reportedly came
OL,9,Fto light.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
